"""
=============================================================
  CRIME SIGHT NOIR — Python Flask Backend
  Equivalent to server.js (Express.js → Python Flask)

  All datasets converted from JavaScript to Python:
    - SEED_STATIONS  (25 police stations)
    - SEED_OFFICERS  (20 officers)
    - SEED_CRIMINALS (11 criminals)
    - SEED_CASES     (75 FIR cases)

  API Routes:
    Core:
      GET  /api/stations
      GET  /api/stations/<id>/cases   ← 4-table JOIN
      GET  /api/cases                 ?severity ?status ?state ?psCode
      GET  /api/stats

    v2 Features:
      POST /api/auth/login
      GET  /api/officers
      GET  /api/officers/<id>/cases   ← 3-table JOIN
      GET  /api/criminals             ?q=search
      GET  /api/criminals/<id>        ← criminal + stations mini-map
      POST /api/criminals
      POST /api/cases
      GET  /api/analytics

  DB : SQLite (via Python built-in sqlite3 module)
  Run: pip install flask flask-cors
       python backend.py
=============================================================
"""

